{"word":"H8080 - שָׁמַן - shâman - shaw-man' - Become fat","slug":"H8080","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁמַן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shâman"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shaw-man'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Become fat"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05DE;&#x05DF; - sha&#x0302;man</b> - <i>shaw-man'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>shine</i>, that is, (by analogy) <i>be</i> (causatively <i>make</i>) <i>oily</i> or <i>gross: - </i>become (make, wax) fat."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4924\">H4924</a>, <a href=\"#/H4925\">H4925</a>, <a href=\"#/H8081\">H8081</a>, <a href=\"#/H8082\">H8082</a>, <a href=\"#/H820\">H820</a>"}]}